This is an example application for accessing the SmartThings platform (http://smartthings.com).  

This is a standard Titanium application build with the Alloy framework.  

It uses the ti.smart module to access the set of SmartThings REST API's.  

Source for the ti.smart module can be found here: https://github.com/alanleard/ti.smart

Documentation for the SmartThings Platform can be found here: https://docs.google.com/a/222wine.com/document/d/1dAoqlmv2EVcbrZsjKV2ksMxNpjV5GNLxzqN6lBxi_UE
